WEBVTT

14:22.149 --> 14:24.066
That also opens
the door for remakes.

14:24.566 --> 14:26.024
Let's not waste time, Rajan.
Let's go.

14:26.066 --> 14:28.316
Sir, I couldn't get tickets
for the film. I need four.

14:28.316 --> 14:30.024
Just let Rajan know
which theatre you're going to.

14:30.066 --> 14:32.233
-Rani, I'm heading out.
-Sir, about the matter I came for...
